name: The Making of Show Me Tomorrow Digital Documentary
description: I decided to film the process of recording SMT and this digital documentary is the result! You will be emailed a link via Hightail.com within 1-2 days of placing your order! Click on the link, download it, watch, and enjoy!

name: JS Instrumental Music Collection
description:
For the first time ever, you can now purchase the instrumental music for over 50 Jamestown Story songs!


Q. What does instrumental music mean you ask?
A. That just means that the music has ALL of the vocals taken out, so it literally is just the instruments to the song.
Q. What could I use this for?
A. Great question! You can bring the instrumentals to your next Karoke get together, throw them on your stereo while your grandparents are over, listen to them when you're in an elevator, or just jam along with each song on your guitar! The possibilities are endless!


You will receive instrumental music for all songs on the following albums:
-Show Me Tomorrow
-Find A Way
-Love vs. Life
-A Walk Through Time
-The Prologue EP
-Never Enough EP
and
-The Nashville Sessions EP (2 JS Songs & Come Back Home)


Once ordered, a download file will be emailed to you via Hightail.com (jamestownstory@gmail.com) in which you'll be able to download the songs! Email jamestownstory@gmail.com if you have any questions!

name: Jamestown Story Wedding Songs
description:
UPDATED PACKAGE!
MORE VERSIONS INCLUDED!


Looking for a song to sing for an upcoming wedding? Look no further!


With this newly designed package, if you don't have someone to sing with, you can sing to the male or female only vocal version! Or if you do have a partner to sing with you can use the instrumental only version!


This package includes an album, instrumental, male vocal only, as well as an only female vocal version: so basically, you'll be getting 8 MP3's total!


Includes the following:

-Dreaming of This feat. Whitney Wiatt (Album Version MP3)
-Dreaming of This feat. Whitney Wiatt (Instrumental MP3)
-Dreaming of This feat. Whitney Wiatt (Male Vox Only MP3)
-Dreaming of This feat. Whitney Wiatt (Female Vox Only MP3)

&

-When You Say feat. Michelle Rene (EP Version MP3)
-When You Say feat. Michelle Rene (Instrumental MP3)
-When You Say feat. Michelle Rene (Male Vox Only MP3)
-When You Say feat. Michelle Rene (Female Vox Only MP3)


You'll also receive lyrics for each song, as well as the piano chords used!
***The piano chords are only chords, not sheet music!***


After the order has been placed you will receive an email containing a download link from Hightail.com within 1-2 days! Click on the link, download the zip file, and you'll be all set!
***If you don't see an email with the link within 1-2 days check your SPAM folder: they end up there sometimes!***


Email jamestownstory@gmail.com if you have any questions about the package and I'd be happy to help!
